snippet.title: Their finest Hour: Battle of Britain Old PCGame
snippet.description:
Thier finest hour: Battle of Britain by Lucasfilm Games was released in 1989 !
Another great game by Lawrence Holland.
Playing a single mission with the Spitfire, Engage the Luftwaffe´s Ace Werner Mölders ( the BF109 with the red nose )... wasn´t to difficult ;-)
